.post
  .post__left-col
    %a.post__img-link{ :href => article }
      = image_tag asset_path("post_sample_image.png"), class: "post__img"
  .post__right-col
    %a.post__catgr{ :href => "#" } Books
    %h1.post__header
      = link_to title_for_fp(article.title), article
    .post__data
      %span.post__data-item Star rating
      %span.post__data-item= pluralize(article.reading_time_in_mins, "minute")
      %span.post__data-item
        %a{ :href => "#" }= article.user.first_name + " " + article.user.last_name
    %a.post__body{ :href => article }
      Dolor repudiandae sed quam eaque natus. Voluptatibus possimus eum blanditiis iste fugit Aspernatur perspiciatis ipsam autem quae modi Necessitatibus.
      %span.post__read-more Read More
